lead_paragraph: Alabama, Ohio State, Michigan and Clemson held the top four spots in the College Football Playoff rankings for the second straight week and Washington moved up a spot to fifth this week.

headline.print_headline: Latest Playoff Rankings Look Promising for Ohio State
